episodes.description:
Nigerian Musicians And The Cult Group They Belong To!
In this video we look in the Nigerian musicians such as Davido, Burna boy, Wizkid, Olamide and more we show you which confraternities they belong; some are in black axe confraternity or neo black movement. Others are in Airlord Confraternity or Eiye, while most are in by  Buccaneers Confraternity and many also belong to the pirate Confraternity and more
